From 13b61563b867d54b7e119daf319fda2075b13953 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Jul 2026 11:18:51 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] refactor(admin): merge delete-movie-dialog and
 delete-series-dialog

- delete-movie-dialog.tsx and delete-series-dialog.tsx were byte-for-byte
  identical apart from the prop name (movieTitle/seriesTitle) and two
  words of copy (Movie/Series, plus series' extra cascade-delete sentence).
- Replace both with a single delete-entity-dialog.tsx taking
  entityLabel, entityName, and an optional extraWarning string, so the
  series-specific 'This will also delete all seasons and episodes.'
  warning is preserved via a prop instead of a forked component.
- Update admin/movies/page.tsx and admin/series/page.tsx call sites.

Net: -55 / +21 lines, one fewer file to keep in sync when the delete
dialog's styling or copy changes. Verified with tsc --noEmit (clean)
and eslint (clean, no new warnings).
---
 ...ie-dialog.tsx => delete-entity-dialog.tsx} | 18 +++++---
 src/app/admin/delete-series-dialog.tsx        | 43 -------------------
 src/app/admin/movies/page.tsx                 |  7 +--
 src/app/admin/series/page.tsx                 |  8 ++--
 4 files changed, 21 insertions(+), 55 deletions(-)
 rename src/app/admin/{delete-movie-dialog.tsx => delete-entity-dialog.tsx} (62%)
 delete mode 100644 src/app/admin/delete-series-dialog.tsx

